definitions.definition: A soft membraneous spot on the head of a baby due to incomplete fusion of the cranial bones .
A structural component of some woodwind instruments, such as recorders and shawms, resembling a barrel with holes bored into it, designed to protect the keywork and to allow the sound to project.
